6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ChatGPT and Jasper Chat share a solid foundation of core features including File Upload, Api Access, Memory, Multilingual. Where ChatGPT pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Web Search and Code Execution and Image Generation and Voice Input and Plugins, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ChatGPT holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Jasper Chat scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, ChatGPT offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Jasper Chat's starting price of $49/mo. ChatGPT has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Jasper Chat does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
